02:08:59,980 --> 02:09:03,310
She was worried something might
happen. She told me about Dave.

1667
02:09:03,480 --> 02:09:06,320
Told me what she told you.
What kind of wife...

1668
02:09:06,480 --> 02:09:09,650
...says that about her husband?
And why'd she run to you?

1669
02:09:09,820 --> 02:09:13,990
[JIMMY] Why didn't you call?
- Because it's like I told the girls.

1670
02:09:14,410 --> 02:09:16,660
Their daddy's a king.

1671
02:09:16,830 --> 02:09:21,080
And a king knows what to do
and does it.

1672
02:09:21,250 --> 02:09:22,830
Even when it's hard.

1673
02:09:23,000 --> 02:09:27,380
And their daddy will do whatever
he has to for those he loves.

1674
02:09:27,550 --> 02:09:30,340
And that's all that matters.

1675
02:09:35,220 --> 02:09:38,890
Because everyone is weak, Jimmy.

1676
02:09:39,060 --> 02:09:41,350
Everyone but us.

1677
02:09:41,520 --> 02:09:43,690
We will never be weak.

1678
02:09:43,850 --> 02:09:46,020
And you...

1679
02:09:46,940 --> 02:09:49,610
You could rule this town.

1680
02:09:53,410 --> 02:09:56,030
And after, Jimmy...

1681
02:09:56,200 --> 02:09:58,950
...let's take the girls down to the parade.

1682
02:09:59,120 --> 02:10:01,870
Katie would have liked that.

1683
02:10:16,550 --> 02:10:18,390
[Marching Band Playing]

1684
02:10:18,550 --> 02:10:20,060
[Cheering]

1685
02:11:38,890 --> 02:11:40,800
Michael!

1686
02:11:41,470 --> 02:11:45,680
Michael! Michael!

1687
02:11:46,980 --> 02:11:51,480
Michael!